{"tid":630361,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)猛火爆2 死硬5 猛龍怪客","createTime":"2018-04-15T14:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T18:27:27.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b116170e20a3e912e0e5e70173193f2fa96b4829","tid":630361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=4vOZNDDNR%2Fo7m4EIcyw%2BPL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=138a44b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=4vOZNDDNR%2Fo7m4EIcyw%2BPL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=85b5092a\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=4vOZNDDNR%2Fo7m4EIcyw%2BPL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e88e12b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9e/RED_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9e%2FRED_2_poster.jpg&h=3c316e90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/19/A_Good_Day_to_Die_Hard.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F19%2FA_Good_Day_to_Die_Hard.jpg&h=1cf83d20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ib8C3Io5KS0/Wk-GvgYmVCI/AAAAAAAAVGI/D6lQvn7tUPMv7Bie_Bv2lItPWxNpNNQ5QCLcBGAs/s1600/death-wish-bruce-willis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ib8C3Io5KS0%2FWk-GvgYmVCI%2FAAAAAAAAVGI%2FD6lQvn7tUPMv7Bie_Bv2lItPWxNpNNQ5QCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fdeath-wish-bruce-willis.jpg&h=99a74277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.出生入死、爾虞我詐的諜報世界裡，你要相信薑是老的辣！退而不休，寶刀未老的探員法蘭克（布魯斯威利 飾）憑著往昔經驗和過人能耐，將與他的昔日戰友再度出手，不但要拯救世界免於核子威脅，更要保全他們自己的老命...<br />\n<br />\n2.由布魯斯威利所飾演的這位超級「平凡英雄」約翰麥克連前往俄羅斯首都莫斯科，開始了一段讓人難以喘息的火爆旅程，老爸希望將闖禍的兒子帶回美國，卻意外發現，傑克是在當地為美國的CIA執行一項空中監獄的任務，他必須要及時化解一場可能發生的核武搶劫災難，迫使這對原本就意見不合的父子必須一起出生入死，他們一定要共同合作，衝出危險，即使個性迥異，衝突不斷，卻也因為血濃於水的親情，開始合作無間，共同解決一觸即發的災難..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述當原本一個位在芝加哥的幸福美滿的家庭遭歹徒闖入，女主人為此喪命，而女兒則遭到強暴、在心中蒙上陰影。這使得該家庭的男主人保羅感到悲痛欲絕，在警方靠不住的情況下，他決定化身為殘酷的私刑者，並不計一切代價追擊兇手；與此同時，他也就此成為了伸張私刑正義的街頭英雄..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=4vOZNDDNR%2Fo7m4EIcyw%2BPL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f65b09bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=4vOZNDDNR%2Fo7m4EIcyw%2BPL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=40627302\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7